reviews.text: Good food.
Great Price Great Food Zero Service, dont complain, just enjoy.🤪

Set lunch for HKD 42!! My set of steamed pork patty was delicious. My friend had beef brisket. The people there were very friendly. I could not speak Cantonese but they helped me out! Oh and the salty fish fried rice was also super. The backroom was spacious! Where can you get a drink, a soup, and a nice rice dish for lunch at this price? 6 stars!!
Enjoyed the unique Hongkong style brunch, nice food and a nice price. Highly recommended.
Good for a quick lunch.  Cheap and tasty.

reviews.text: 牛腩不錯😋
是中上環一間普通的茶餐廳，但食物尚可,例湯好像沒有味精,在中上環地區算是價錢合理的茶餐廳，環境就一般，尚算舒服｡
40蚊左右有飯有湯有飲品已經難得喇…一般茶記格局唔好苛求吧，豉油雞、鹽焗雞飯係餐廳嘅主打！Good呀！
